Product boundary used for this evaluation:
- “AI matching” means Candidate-owned deriveCandidateJobSignals guidance only. It cannot hide or reorder jobs, affect Eligibility/Queue/Attention, or enter an Employer projection.
- “Candidate answer scoring” was not implemented or tested as an overall score. The evaluated output is one criterion-local SUPPORTED / CONTRADICTED / NOT_ADDRESSED / INSUFFICIENT_EVIDENCE finding per sealed criterion.
- Employer assistance means source-linked Summary, criterion findings, exact quotes, still_unknown, Reviewer Questions, and neutral Process Context. It cannot decide, rank, advance, reject, or release a Slot.

