Implementation changes exercised:
- LIVE adapters accept an explicit model constructor option. Their defaults remain gpt-5.6-luna/low and gpt-5.6-sol/medium.
- OPENAI_EVAL_MODEL is read only by the two LIVE eval files. Worker composition passes no model override and does not read this environment variable.
- Candidate discovery Prompt advanced to 1.0.2 with explicit ready/abstain and per-signal branch rules.
- Employer Analyst Prompt advanced to 1.0.4 with zero-based exact-quote indexing, four-state evidence-array rules, PROCESS field separation, and injection no-echo rules.
- SDK-side Zod refinement errors now map to permanent AI_SCHEMA_MISMATCH instead of retryable AI_PROVIDER_UNAVAILABLE.
- Deterministic Employer prohibition failures now expose a safe policy code, never model text.

